        {
            "title": "珍惜生命│灣仔合和中心男子高處墮下 倒臥扶手電梯當場不治",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"墮樓男子倒臥扶手電梯上死亡。梁國峰攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/a20e383b5835ccf3681ea8311e34a763/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250222/_2025022211501543744.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">墮樓男子倒臥扶手電梯上死亡。梁國峰攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>灣仔皇后大道東183號合和中心，今（22日）早上10時57分，一名男子被發現倒臥在扶手電梯上，昏迷不醒，警員接報到場，經調查後相信男事主由高處墮下，跌落扶手電梯上，救護員經檢驗後證實事主當場不治。警方正調查事主身份及其墮樓原因。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4096641/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"墮樓男子倒臥扶手電梯上死亡。梁國峰攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a69c09162a65da2c479e7c67b40de3d8/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250222_114321851_02.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        墮樓男子倒臥扶手電梯上死亡。梁國峰攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4096642/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警員到場調查。梁國峰攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/61cfc3008dbb112e9c2be6921931a22b/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250222_114321851_03.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警員到場調查。梁國峰攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4096643/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5cc48be3585bb270eee899051b164001/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250222_114321851_04.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>自殺求助熱線：<br/>\n「情緒通」精神健康支援熱線：18111 <br/>\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222<br/>\n生命熱線： 2382 0000<br/>\n明愛向晴軒： 18288<br/>\n社會福利署： 2343 2255<br/>\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000<br/>\n東華三院芷若園： 18281<br/>\n醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350<br/>\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open 噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk/\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.openup.hk</a>\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2054261/即時-港聞-珍惜生命│灣仔合和中心男子高處墮下-倒臥扶手電梯當場不治",
